    • Method Detail

      • apply

        public xsbti.Position apply(xsbti.Position position)
        Performs mapping from the position in generated source file to the position in original source file it was generated from.

        If no position in original source file can be found, input position is returned.
        Position in source file cannot be found in two cases:
        • file was not generated,
        • no appropriate mapper was configured.
        Parameters:
        position - compilation error/warning position in generated file
        Returns:
        position in source file or input position if no source position can be found
